OL,3,CRyanair to close check-in 20 minutes
OL,4,Cearlier after EU border control chaos
OL,6,FRyanair passengers will have a shorter
OL,7,Fwindow to use airport check-in or bag
OL,8,Fdrop services as the budget airline
OL,9,Fchanges its rules later this year.
OL,11,FThe airline has announced that it will
OL,12,Fclose these services one hour before
OL,13,Fthe scheduled departure of a flight,
OL,14,Fup from 40 minutes currently.
OL,16,FIt said this change will give
OL,17,Fpassengers more time to get through
OL,18,Fsecurity and passport checks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
