OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776960675
OL,3,CRyanair to close check-in 20 minutes
OL,4,Cearlier after EU border control chaos
OL,6,FThe announcement comes after the full
OL,7,Fimplementation of the European Union's
OL,8,Fnew Entry/Exit system (EES), which,
OL,9,Fdespite being designed to be more
OL,10,Fefficient, has caused chaotic delays
OL,11,Fin some airports in recent weeks.
OL,13,FMore than 100 easyJet passengers stuck
OL,14,Fin delays at passport desks at Milan
OL,15,FLinate airport missed a flight to
OL,16,FManchester earlier this month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
