OL,3,CRyanair to close check-in 20 minutes
OL,4,Cearlier after EU border control chaos
OL,6,FRyanair claims its new policy, which
OL,7,Fcomes into place from November 10,
OL,8,Fwill reduce the "very small number of
OL,9,Fpassengers" who miss their flight
OL,10,Fwhile stuck in queues.
OL,12,FIt warns on its website that
OL,13,Fpassengers who fail to check in on
OL,14,Ftime "may be denied boarding without
OL,15,Frefund", adding that travellers will
OL,16,Fstill be able to check in online until
OL,17,Ftwo hours before departure.
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@KO]vD@FOUwD@GO]
