OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776960675
OL,3,CRyanair to close check-in 20 minutes
OL,4,Cearlier after EU border control chaos
OL,6,FRyanair chief marketing officer Dara
OL,7,FBrady said the "small 20-minute
OL,8,Fchange" will "allow these 20% of our
OL,9,Fcustomers who check in a bag more time
OL,10,Fto clear through airport security and
OL,11,Fpassport queues, and get to their
OL,12,Fdeparture gate on time".
OL,14,FHe added that this will be
OL,15,Fparticularly important "during busy
OL,16,Ftravel periods when some of these
OL,17,Fairport queues can be longer".
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@GO]pD@NOUtD@WO]wD@XOUyD@]O]
